@startuml task_lifecycle
title Standalone Task Lifecycle

[*] --> Queued : create task

Queued --> Active : assign worker
Active --> Completed : complete
Active --> Cancelled : cancel

Completed --> [*]
Cancelled --> [*]

note right of Queued
  Task waiting for a worker
  to pick it up
end note

note right of Active
  Worker is executing
  the task
end note

note right of Completed
  Task finished successfully
  Entity can be removed
end note

note right of Cancelled
  Task terminated
  Resources released
  Game handles consequences
end note

@enduml
